<p>so i started writing this as a bit, just to get funny screencaps of MCD and the Factory pinkwashing themselves, and then i decided to actually make it a tale, and then Kinch came up with the idea that gave it a plot instead of being just some funny tweets, so here we are. this tale is dedicated to queer liberation and the anticapitalist agenda; i hope it makes some people angry.</p>
<p>Read <a href="/scp-4493">SCP-4493</a> for the continuation of the story.</p>
<p>the tweet template is originally from <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561391057" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span>'s <a href="/intermission">Intermission</a></p>
